1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,011
Practice these three procedures to help yourself think about trivialities.

2
00:00:05,011 --> 00:00:06,371
1.

3
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:09,730
Keep your eyes focused on the big objective.

4
00:00:09,920 --> 00:00:14,051
Many times, we're like the salesman who, failing to make the sale,

5
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:19,250
reports to his manager, yes, but I sure convinced the customer he was wrong.

6
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:24,451
In selling, the big objective is winning sales, not arguments.

7
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:33,730
In marriage, the big objective is peace, happiness, tranquility, not winning quarrels or saying, I could have told you so.

8
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:42,770
In working with employees, the big objective is developing their full potential, not making issues out of their minor errors.

9
00:00:43,281 --> 00:00:54,051
In living with neighbors, the big objective is mutual respect and friendship, not seeing if you can have their dog impounded because once in a while it barks at night.

10
00:00:54,720 --> 00:01:03,411
Paraphrasing some military lingo, it is much better to lose a battle and win the war than to win a battle and lose the war.

11
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:07,011
Resolve to keep your eyes on the big ball.

12
00:01:07,011 --> 00:01:08,690
2.

13
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:11,571
Ask, is it really important?

14
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:19,411
Before becoming negatively excited, just ask yourself, is it important enough for me to get all worked up about?

15
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:25,571
There is no better way to avoid frustration over petty matters than to use this medicine.

16
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:33,571
At least 90% of quarrels and feuds would never take place if we just faced troublesome situations with,

17
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,810
is this really important?

18
00:01:36,881 --> 00:01:40,531
Three, don't fall into the triviality trap.

19
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:49,091
In making speeches, solving problems, counseling employees, think of those things that really matter, things that make the difference.

20
00:01:49,281 --> 00:01:52,531
Don't become submerged under surface issues.

21
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:55,091
Concentrate on important things.

